{"id": "1179682185024913508", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "694573382380945529", "author_name": "craux.", "content": "do we have pvp yet?", "timestamp": "2023-11-30T07:15:50.345000+00:00"}
{"id": "1179682494937837678", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "author_id": "1164258265799086080", "author_name": "metam0n", "content": "Basic Rules:\n1. your team contains 4 characters, each character has a \"color\". Now, Yellow faction could combined with other 3 color, team only 4 yellow faction perform yellow's feature.\n\n2. yellow's feature help you not that easy to die, and accelerate you Ultimate Ability. blue's feature is some tentacle automatically attack the front enemy. Red's feature is a special card that could make character's Ultimate Ability change into different form, or just using like a consumables to accelerate your Ultimate Ability. Purple, the first card you play at each turn will be copy into a stack, if the cards in the stack is equal to 5, you earn a extra round, you could use those card you copy into the stack at that extra round.\n\n3. each characters has a Ultimate Ability, when in a battle, related UI displayed on the left top. When 100 energy is enough, icons would be active. Play related [strike] or [defense] or some specific card could get Ultimate Ability energy.\n\n4. your team has a KeySkill, need 1000 energy. related UI displayed on the left bottom. when you play a card that cost was not 0, you got cost*factor points energy.\n\n5. your team has a Death Resistant, showing at the right top. three icons here were Death Resistant chance, enemy's total damage current round, round counter. When your HP less then 0 will judge if Death Resistant is trigger, if so, stay at 1 HP, and Death Resistant be half.\n\n6.Basically, each turn you would draw 5 cards and have 5 cost point, and up to 10 cards in hand. you could change these by items during a quest.\n\n7. Each characters could equip 1 密契 and 2 命轮. 密契 system was unlock after Lv.35 account, the second 命轮 is release at Lv.15 account. These were important part of your build.", "timestamp": "2023-11-30T07:17:04.234000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-30T07:30:28.965000+00:00"}
